CHANGELOG

Project         :	IronClad
Author          :	George Kudrayvtsev
Current Version	:	1.2.2 alpha
Last Updated	:	02.21.2013

Version 1.2.2a (02.21.2013):
 *  Font library cleanup
 +  Font string caching support
 +  GUI button support in progress
 +  Windows MessageBox popup on errors
 +  Toggling stdout logs

Version 1.2.1a (02.10.2013):
 +  Mesh rotation support (in progress)
 +  Mesh horizontal / vertical flipping support
 +  Animation entities support sprite sheet override
 +  New shader for animation
 *  Animatable entities are physical objects now
 *  Animation bug fixes 
 *  Player spawn loads in level properly
 *  Actual player is not created on player spawn, meaning that the player
    sprite, when specified as an attribute in the level editor, is not
    actually used, and is merely a placeholder for the location.
    The actual player animations / sprite(s) should be loaded separately
    from the engine. 

Version 1.2.0a (02.09.2013):
 +  Animation beta stage complete
 *  Modified default fragment shader to accept texture coordinate offset

Version 1.1.6a (02.08.2013):
 *  Improved asset loading and logging
 *  Animation support improved

Version 1.1.5a (02.07.2013):
 +  Animation support begun
 +  Texture assets can load sub-images
 +  Scene can render as wire-mesh
 +  Fancier debug logging
 *  Scene bug fixes
 *  Minor font bug fix, '~' bitmap loads now 

Version 1.1.0a (02.03.2013):
 +  TrueType font rendering added

Version 1.0.7a (02.02.2013):
 +  Querying for scene camera
 +  Fonts are being worked on, almost functional

Version 1.0.6a (02.01.2013):
 +  More IronClad identifiers for key and mouse codes
 +  Insert meshes into scenes easily, from file or existing

Version 1.0.5a (01.25.2013):
 *  Updated binaries
 *  Fixed level loading
 *  Physics bugfixes

Version 1.0.4a (01.21.2013):
 *  Fixed physics bugs
 *  Fixed vector rotation bugs

Version 1.0.3a (01.17.2013):
 +  Level contains more world info
 +  Physics bug fixes

Version 1.0.2a (01.16.2013):
 +	Texture overrides
 +	Basic physics
 *	Bug fixes

Version 1.0.1a (01.14.2013):
 *	Improved level loading

Version 1.0.0a (01.10.2013):
 *	Initial commit
